What is S3 ?

it is a simple storage service where we store any amount of data and acess it any time anywhere over the internet

Features:

Static website hosting: We can host the static website to enable this feature it provides specific website URL
Transfer acceleration: its provides speeds up upload/download of the objects using edge locations
Create replication rule: we can automatically copy objects from one bucket to another bucket
Storage Classes: We can manage objects retention period

Storages Classes:

Standard
Intelligent-Tiering
Standard-IA
One Zone-IA
Glacier
Deep Glacier
